<div class="content"><nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/servicearea/">Service Area</a> › Fleet Wraps Lombard</nav><h1>Fleet Wraps Lombard, IL</h1><p class="lead speakable">Chicago Fleet Wraps provides professional fleet vehicle wrap services to businesses in Lombard, IL and surrounding DuPage County communities. Known for its central location along the I-88 corridor and Roosevelt Road, Lombard gives wrapped fleet vehicles massive daily exposure across the western suburbs. We wrap cargo vans, box trucks, sprinter vans, and pickup trucks using Avery Dennison MPI 1105 and 3M IJ180-CV3 premium cast vinyl. Free pickup and delivery. 2-year workmanship warranty. Fleet discounts available for 3+ vehicles.</p>
<p class="pricing_intro_added" style="margin-top:16px">Lombard businesses operating along Route 53, I-88, and the East-West Tollway benefit from exceptional fleet wrap ROI. Vehicles wrapped with your brand identity generate 30,000–70,000 impressions daily in DuPage County's dense commercial corridors. With fleet discounts available for 3+ vehicles, Lombard companies can brand their entire fleet for less than a single month of traditional advertising.</p><div class="trust"><span>📅 <strong>24+ Years</strong> Experience</span><span>🏆 <strong>9,400+</strong> Vehicles Wrapped</span><span>✅ <strong>Avery Dennison &amp; 3M</strong> Certified</span><span>📍 <strong>Lombard, IL</strong></span><span>🚐 <strong>Free Fleet Pickup</strong></span></div><h2>Why Lombard Is a Great Market for Fleet Wraps</h2><p class="body-text">Lombard's strategic position between Elmhurst and Wheaton puts it at the center of DuPage County's busiest commercial and residential corridors. Roosevelt Road, one of the highest-traffic arterials in the western suburbs, runs directly through Lombard — meaning a wrapped service van driving to a job site gains thousands of additional impressions from passing motorists, shoppers at Yorktown Center, and residents throughout the village.</p><p class="body-text">With a population of over 44,000 and a housing stock that includes both older homes and new construction, Lombard generates year-round demand for home services. HVAC companies, plumbers, electricians, and landscapers with wrapped vehicles report significantly higher brand recognition and inbound calls compared to unmarked trucks. At $0.04–$0.07 per thousand impressions, fleet wraps are the most cost-effective advertising investment for Lombard-area businesses.</p><h2>Fleet Wrap Services for Lombard</h2><ul class="services"><li><strong>Cargo Van Wraps</strong> — Full and partial wraps for Ford Transit, Ram ProMaster, Chevy Express. Starting at $3,150.</li><li><strong>Box Truck Wraps</strong> — 16–26 ft box trucks with high-impact side and rear graphics. Starting at $4,500.</li><li><strong>Sprinter Van Wraps</strong> — Standard and high-roof Mercedes Sprinter wraps. Starting at $3,700.</li><li><strong>Pickup Truck Wraps</strong> — F-150, Ram 1500, Silverado wraps for contractors and trades.</li><li><strong>Fleet Programs</strong> — Volume discounts: 5% (3–4 vehicles), 10% (5–9), 15% (10+).</li><li><strong>Color Change Wraps</strong> — Matte, gloss, satin, and specialty finishes for personal and commercial vehicles.</li></ul><h2>Industries We Serve in Lombard</h2><ul class="services"><li><strong>HVAC Companies</strong> — Furnace, AC, and ductwork contractors wrapping service vans for year-round visibility.</li><li><strong>Plumbing</strong> — Residential and commercial plumbers building brand recognition across DuPage County.</li><li><strong>Electricians</strong> — Panel upgrades, rewiring, and EV charger installation companies.</li><li><strong>Landscaping</strong> — Lawn care, tree service, and snow removal companies wrapping trucks and trailers.</li><li><strong>General Contractors</strong> — Home renovation, remodeling, and new construction companies.</li><li><strong>Restaurants &amp; Catering</strong> — Food delivery, catering vans, and food truck wraps.</li></ul><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="faq-item"><h3>Do you offer free pickup in Lombard?</h3><p>Yes — we provide free fleet pickup and delivery throughout Lombard and all of DuPage County. Our Chicago facility is approximately 25 minutes from downtown Lombard via I-290 or I-88.</p>
<figure class="supp-image-block"><img src="/images/cfw_van_1.webp" alt="Vehicle wraps Lombard IL" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="420"><figcaption>Vehicle wraps Lombard IL — Chicago Fleet Wraps · (312) 597-1286</figcaption></figure>
</div><div class="faq-item"><h3>How much do fleet wraps cost for Lombard businesses?</h3><p>Cargo van wraps start at $3,150, sprinter vans at $3,700, and box trucks at $4,500. Fleet discounts of 5–15% apply for businesses wrapping 3 or more vehicles. All fleet wraps are 100% tax deductible under IRS Section 179.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>How long do fleet wraps last?</h3><p>Our wraps use premium cast vinyl rated for 5–7 years of outdoor durability. Combined with our 2-year installation warranty covering lifting, peeling, and bubbling, your investment is fully protected for years of commercial use.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>Can I wrap leased vehicles?</h3><p>Absolutely. Vinyl wraps are non-permanent and can be professionally removed without any damage to the original paint. Many Lombard businesses wrap leased cargo vans and return them in pristine condition at lease end.</p></div><div class="faq-item">
<h3>How long does a fleet wrap last on a Lombard delivery vehicle?</h3>
<p>Using Avery Dennison MPI 1105 or 3M IJ180-CV3 cast vinyl, fleet wraps last 5–7 years under normal conditions. For high-mileage Lombard delivery vehicles, we recommend a UV-protective overlaminate that extends the wrap's appearance and protects against Illinois sun exposure.</p>
</div>
<div class="faq-item">
<h3>Can you wrap our Lombard fleet vehicles at our location?</h3>
<p>We offer free pickup and delivery for all Lombard fleet wrap projects — we come to your Lombard facility, pick up the vehicles, wrap them at our Chicago shop, and return them. For large fleets, we can also arrange on-site installation at your Lombard location.</p>
</div>
